      <p class="svc-detail-quote">"Carpet should feel like home the moment you step on it. We make sure <em>every seam, every edge, and every corner</em> is done right."</p>

      <p class="svc-detail-body">Our team handles full carpet replacement projects as well -- removing old, worn carpet and underpad, prepping the subfloor, and laying new carpet that fits perfectly. We are not satisfied until the lines are clean, the corners are tight, and the finish is seamless.</p>

